title: Hazardous Waste Locations, Washington DC, 2002
name: Hazardous Waste Locations, Washington DC, 2002
description:
Hazardous Waste locations. The dataset contains locations and attributes of Hazardous Waste, created as part of the DC Geographic Information System (DC GIS) for the D.C. Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO) and participating D.C. government agencies.

A database provided by the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) identified Hazardous Waste locations. All DC GIS data is stored and exported in Maryland State Plane coordinates NAD 83 meters.
